        "sendBody": true,
        "specifyBody": "json",
        "jsonBody": "{\"model\": \"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001\", \"max_tokens\": 1500, \"messages\": [{\"role\": \"user\", \"content\": \"[재무 트렌드 분석가] 종목: {{$json.ticker}}\\n검색 결과(10-K/10-Q):\\n{{$json.context}}\\n\\n3~5년(또는 12~20분기) 기준으로 다음을 표로 정리하라:\\n- 매출, YoY, GM, OM, OCF, Capex, FCF, FCF마진, 주식수\\n- 변곡점 Top 3 + 원인 태그 [가격/물량][제품믹스][원가/공급망][마케팅/판관비][환율][일회성][규모][규제][매크로]\\n- 모든 주장에 [출처: 문서/페이지] 형식 인용 필수\\n\\nJSON으로만 응답:\\n{\\n  \\\"summary\\\": \\\"2~3줄 요약\\\",\\n  \\\"trend_table\\\": [{\\\"period\\\":\\\"...\\\",\\\"revenue\\\":\\\"...\\\",\\\"yoy\\\":\\\"...\\\",\\\"gm\\\":\\\"...\\\",\\\"om\\\":\\\"...\\\",\\\"fcf\\\":\\\"...\\\"}],\\n  \\\"inflections\\\": [{\\\"metric\\\":\\\"...\\\",\\\"when\\\":\\\"...\\\",\\\"cause_tag\\\":\\\"...\\\",\\\"source\\\":\\\"...\\\"}],\\n  \\\"leading_indicators\\\": [\\\"...\\\"]\\n}\"}]}",
