        "jsonBody": "{\"model\": \"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001\", \"max_tokens\": 1500, \"messages\": [{\"role\": \"user\", \"content\": \"[Moat 분석가 — 버핏/멍거 스타일] 종목: {{$json.ticker}}\\n검색 결과(10-K Business / Competition):\\n{{$json.context}}\\n\\n해자 유형은 제한 없음. 후보 발굴 → 증거 강도(강/중/약) → Moat Grade(A/B/C/D). 출처 인용 필수.\\n\\nJSON:\\n{\\n  \\\"moat_grade\\\": \\\"A|B|C|D\\\",\\n  \\\"core_moats\\\": [{\\\"name\\\":\\\"...\\\",\\\"category\\\":\\\"...\\\",\\\"evidence_strength\\\":\\\"강|중|약\\\",\\\"reason\\\":\\\"...\\\",\\\"source\\\":\\\"...\\\"}],\\n  \\\"erosion_signals\\\": [\\\"...\\\"],\\n  \\\"competition_threats\\\": [{\\\"competitor\\\":\\\"...\\\",\\\"attack_path\\\":\\\"...\\\",\\\"source\\\":\\\"...\\\"}]\\n}\"}]}",
