        "jsonBody": "{\"model\": \"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001\", \"max_tokens\": 1500, \"messages\": [{\"role\": \"user\", \"content\": \"[경영진 약속 이행 검증 감사관] 종목: {{$json.ticker}}\\n검색 결과(주주서한 3년):\\n{{$json.context}}\\n\\n전략적 약속 추출 → 실행 증거 매칭 → 이행 상태(완료/진행중/지연/방향전환/중단). 정직성 등급(A/B/C/D).\\n\\nJSON:\\n{\\n  \\\"honesty_grade\\\": \\\"A|B|C|D\\\",\\n  \\\"promises\\\": [{\\\"promise\\\":\\\"...\\\",\\\"first_mentioned\\\":\\\"...\\\",\\\"status\\\":\\\"완료|진행중|지연|방향전환|중단|모호\\\",\\\"communication_tone\\\":\\\"솔직|부분 인정|회피|외부 탓\\\",\\\"source\\\":\\\"...\\\"}],\\n  \\\"best_kept_top3\\\": [\\\"...\\\"],\\n  \\\"biggest_misses_top3\\\": [\\\"...\\\"]\\n}\"}]}",
