        "jsonBody": "{\"model\": \"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001\", \"max_tokens\": 1500, \"messages\": [{\"role\": \"user\", \"content\": \"[반대의견 분석가] 종목: {{$json.ticker}}\\n검색 결과(전체 소스):\\n{{$json.context}}\\n\\n이 종목에 투자하면 안 되는 이유 12개를 표로. 가장 치명적인 Top 3 별도 표시. 출처 인용 필수.\\n\\nJSON:\\n{\\n  \\\"bear_arguments\\\": [{\\\"argument\\\":\\\"...\\\",\\\"evidence\\\":\\\"...\\\",\\\"financial_impact\\\":\\\"매출|마진|FCF|자본조달\\\",\\\"disprove_with\\\":\\\"...\\\",\\\"source\\\":\\\"...\\\"}],\\n  \\\"most_dangerous_top3\\\": [{\\\"argument\\\":\\\"...\\\",\\\"why_critical\\\":\\\"...\\\",\\\"source\\\":\\\"...\\\"}]\\n}\"}]}",
        "options": {}
      },
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.httpRequest",
