        "sendBody": true,
        "specifyBody": "json",
        "jsonBody": "{\"model\": \"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001\", \"max_tokens\": 1500, \"messages\": [{\"role\": \"user\", \"content\": \"[소스 갭 분석가] 종목: {{$json.ticker}}\\n검색 결과(현재 업로드된 소스):\\n{{$json.context}}\\n\\n주식 리서치에 꼭 필요한 데이터 중 누락 항목을 필수/권장으로 분류. 어디서 얻을 수 있는지.\\n\\nJSON:\\n{\\n  \\\"essential_missing\\\": [{\\\"item\\\":\\\"...\\\",\\\"why_needed\\\":\\\"...\\\",\\\"where_to_get\\\":\\\"10-K|10-Q|IR deck|Investor Day|transcript|경쟁사|산업리포트\\\"}],\\n  \\\"nice_to_have\\\": [{\\\"item\\\":\\\"...\\\",\\\"why_needed\\\":\\\"...\\\",\\\"where_to_get\\\":\\\"...\\\"}],\\n  \\\"next_questions\\\": [\\\"...\\\"]\\n}\"}]}",
        "options": {}
      },
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.httpRequest",
      "typeVersion": 4.2,
      "position": [
